data.title: Sholom Sprouts Music and Me Tickets
data.meta_description: Come with us on a musical journey as we fill the room with rhythm, melody and groove with Timbalooloo!
data.text:
Description

Sprouts with Timbalooloo

5 Tuesdays

October 11, 18, 25 and November 1, 8

11:15 AM – 12:00 PM

For children 6–18 months old

Price: $240 members/$280 non-members

Timbalooloo is an innovative method created by renowned Israeli musician and composer Oran Etkin in which instruments come to life and speak through their music. Come groove with us on a musical journey as we fill the room with rhythm and melody using music by great masters from Herbie Hancock to Tito Puente, Mozart to Willie Nelson and original songs and games to help introduce your baby to music in a fun and intuitive way. Join us for a musical adventure through our fall Jewish holidays!
